    Pure RESO Data Dictionary 2.0 canonical schema for the 12 Resources Atlas uses:
    Property, Member, Office, Contacts, OpenHouse, Showing, ShowingAppointment,
    HistoryTransactional, InternetTracking, Media, PropertyRooms, PropertyUnitTypes.

    No Atlas-specific decisions baked in. Atlas adapts this canonical in PR0.5.
  '''
}

